<p><b>4.</b> Environmental integration, <b>AR</b>.</p>
<p>Well, this is my favorite part. These days transparent displays begin to appear, and in 4-6 years their quality is expected to be great and they will be able to be used on streets with the usual lighting conditions. Speaking of the third paragraph's point, a transparent display can "mix" the virtual space with the reality behind it. Virtual character wouldn't be standing on the virtual floor, but on the real floor behind the screen. It would provide huge AR possibilities.</p>
